description:
Let's retrace here the colonization by Europeans, from the discovery by Christopher Columbus until the end of the Seven Years’ War. 
-------- 
If you want to support the channel, here is our Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/geohistory 
-------- 
English translation & voiceover: Matthew Bates https://www.epicvoiceover.com/

08:20 Resistance 
09:33 Rebellion in Peru 
10:22 European competition
